 {"sentiment":0,"breadcrumb":[{"link":"https://help.hackerearth.com/","name":"Help Center"},{"link":"https://help.hackerearth.com/assessments-recruiters","name":"Assessments: Recruiters"}],"humanLanguage":"en","icon":"https://help.hackerearth.com/hubfs/HE_identity.png","diffbotUri":"article|3|4749193","siteName":"hackerearth.com","pageUrl":"https://help.hackerearth.com/hc/en-us/articles/360003878774-format-for-adding-mcqs-in-bulk","html":"<p>You can add multiple MCQs in one go by using an Excel sheet.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Note<\/strong>: The Excel file that you will use to upload MCQs in bulk must be in the <strong>.xls<\/strong> or <strong>.xlsx<\/strong> format only.<\/p>\n<p>The format that you must follow in the Excel sheet is as follows:<\/p>\n<table> <tbody> <tr> <td><strong>S. No.<\/strong><\/td> <td><strong>Column names <\/strong><strong>(in your Excel sheet)<\/strong><\/td> <td><strong>Information to be added in each column<\/strong><\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td> <p>1<\/p> <\/td> <td> <p>Section name<\/p> <\/td> <td> <p>Enter the name of the section in which you want to upload the questions.<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td> <p>2<\/p> <\/td> <td> <p>Problem Statement<\/p> <\/td> <td> <p>Enter your question.<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td> <p>3<\/p> <\/td> <td> <p>Option 1 (mandatory)<\/p> <\/td> <td> <p>Add one of the choices as an answer to your question. It is mandatory to add at least 2 options to an MCQ.<\/p> <\/td> <\/tr> <tr> <td> <p>4<\/p> <\/td> <td> <p>Option 2 (mandatory)<\/p> <\/td> <td> <p>Add one of the choices as an answer to your question.

You can also view the error that the question contains.\nDo not remove or change the header row, however, to add more than four options for an MCQ, create a column next to Option 4 with the header in the same format. For example, Option 5.\nPartial scoring is only allowed for multiple answers. The default value of the partial scoring column is No.","type":"article","title":"Format for adding MCQs in bulk","docId":68052772330,"fromSeedUrl":"https://help.hackerearth.com/","seedUrlHash32":1957119,"parentUrlDocId":83686958532,"gburl":"https://help.hackerearth.com/hc/en-us/articles/360003878774-format-for-adding-mcqs-in-bulk-diffbotxyz2817970821","lastCrawlTimeUTC":1719138144,"timestamp":"Sun, 23 Jun 2024 10:22:24 GMT"}
