 {"sentiment":0,"images":[{"naturalHeight":282,"width":621,"diffbotUri":"image|3|1806293612","url":"https://help.hackerearth.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Knowledge%20Base%20Import/mceclip2-Jan-30-2023-11-44-13-6745-AM.png?width=1863&height=846&name=mceclip2-Jan-30-2023-11-44-13-6745-AM.png","naturalWidth":621,"primary":true,"height":282},{"naturalHeight":223,"width":610,"diffbotUri":"image|3|1044029741","url":"https://help.hackerearth.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Knowledge%20Base%20Import/mceclip6-Jan-30-2023-11-44-12-3406-AM.png?width=1830&height=669&name=mceclip6-Jan-30-2023-11-44-12-3406-AM.png","naturalWidth":610,"height":223}],"originalType":"other","icon":"https://help.hackerearth.com/hubfs/HE_identity.png","diffbotUri":"article|3|-744138556","siteName":"hackerearth.com","type":"article","title":"Sending reminders to candidates","breadcrumb":[{"link":"https://help.hackerearth.com/","name":"Help Center"},{"link":"https://help.hackerearth.com/assessments-recruiters","name":"Assessments: Recruiters"}],"humanLanguage":"en","pageUrl":"https://help.hackerearth.com/hc/en-us/articles/360004258514-sending-reminders-to-candidates","html":"<p>To send reminders of tests to candidates, follow these steps:<\/p>\n<ol> <li>Log in to your HackerEarth Recruit account using your admin credentials.<\/li> <li>Click <strong>Tests<\/strong>.<\/li> <li>Navigate to the test for which you want to send reminders to the candidates.<br><em><br>Note:<\/em> You must publish the test to be able to invite candidates.<\/li> <\/ol>\n<ol> <li>In the <strong>Candidates<\/strong> section, click <strong>Invited<\/strong>.<\/li> <li>Select the candidates to whom you want to send reminders for the test.<br><br><em>Important<\/em><em>:<\/em> You can send reminders to the candidates with the statuses '<strong>Not attempted<\/strong>' or '<strong>Test reset<\/strong>' only.<br><br><figure><img sizes=\"(max-width: 621px) 100vw, 621px\" src=\"https://help.hackerearth.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Knowledge%20Base%20Import/mceclip2-Jan-30-2023-11-44-13-6745-AM.png?width=1863&height=846&name=mceclip2-Jan-30-2023-11-44-13-6745-AM.png\" srcset=\"https://help.hackerearth.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Knowledge%20Base%20Import/mceclip2-Jan-30-2023-11-44-13-6745-AM.png?width=311&height=141&name=mceclip2-Jan-30-2023-11-44-13-6745-AM.png 311w, https://help.hackerearth.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Knowledge%20Base%20Import/mceclip2-Jan-30-2023-11-44-13-6745-AM.png?width=621&height=282&name=mceclip2-Jan-30-2023-11-44-13-6745-AM.png 621w, https://help.hackerearth.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Knowledge%20Base%20Import/mceclip2-Jan-30-2023-11-44-13-6745-AM.png?width=932&height=423&name=mceclip2-Jan-30-2023-11-44-13-6745-AM.png 932w,

To learn more about auto-reminders, read this article.\nHow does auto-reminder work?\nThe first reminder is sent 48 hours after the initial invite if any of the following conditions happen:\nThe candidate hasn\u2019t taken the test.\nThe test invite hasn\u2019t expired.\nThe test End Date is more than 48 hours in the future\nIf either the end date or expiration date is set, a reminder will be sent 24 hours before the test ends or before the invite expires, whichever comes first, if the candidate has not yet taken the test. If both the end date and expiration date are not set, a reminder will be sent one week after the invite was sent if the candidate has not taken the test yet.","docId":179054781951,"fromSeedUrl":"https://help.hackerearth.com/","seedUrlHash32":1957119,"parentUrlDocId":203273692669,"gburl":"https://help.hackerearth.com/hc/en-us/articles/360004258514-sending-reminders-to-candidates-diffbotxyz1810815819","lastCrawlTimeUTC":1719138154,"timestamp":"Sun, 23 Jun 2024 10:22:34 GMT"}
