 {"sentiment":0.181,"originalType":"other","icon":"https://help.hackerearth.com/hubfs/HE_identity.png","diffbotUri":"article|3|-466371144","siteName":"hackerearth.com","type":"article","title":"Do's and don'ts - ML Hackathon","tags":[{"score":0.9040676951408386,"sentiment":0,"count":2,"label":"hackathon","uri":"https://diffbot.com/entity/E4eMjuTQLNEa3XfeyT7nr_w","rdfTypes":["http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Event"]}],"breadcrumb":[{"link":"https://help.hackerearth.com/","name":"Help Center"},{"link":"https://help.hackerearth.com/assessments-recruiters","name":"Assessments: Recruiters"}],"humanLanguage":"en","pageUrl":"https://help.hackerearth.com/dos-and-donts-ml-hackathon","html":"<p>This document details the following for a Machine Learning hackathon with automatic evaluation.<\/p>\n<ul> <li><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1zAv4yOuvRqciCAG3FVvmwYama-rDsEkxWkSC3Y2EmlU/edit#heading=h.u2kk759ayo14\">Mandatory resources<\/a><\/li> <li><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1zAv4yOuvRqciCAG3FVvmwYama-rDsEkxWkSC3Y2EmlU/edit#heading=h.tzy4usj6yb2q\">Do&rsquo;s and don&rsquo;ts<\/a><\/li> <li><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1zAv4yOuvRqciCAG3FVvmwYama-rDsEkxWkSC3Y2EmlU/edit#heading=h.1kul8l1l88y5\">Final checks<\/a><\/li> <\/ul>\n<h3>Mandatory resources<\/h3>\n<h4>Data files<\/h4>\n<ul> <li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/15TJViM01AHjRguG7JCvGXkkLp8MhEKRd/view?usp=share_link\">Train.csv<\/a>: Contains the training data<\/li> <li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1LJtEXp4-8ZAkpqr2T9Nkxh_o9RmLMU8_/view?usp=share_link\">Test.csv<\/a>: Contains the test data (without target column)<\/li> <li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1xEro8LgT-fZVnV3CjLcI1f7YoiagvpnY/view?usp=share_link\">Sample submission.csv<\/a>: Format that candidates must follow for their submission<br><strong>Note<\/strong>: These files (Train,csv, test.csv, and Sample submission.csv) should be included in a single .ZIP file named dataset.

