 {"sentiment":0.949,"images":[{"naturalHeight":333,"width":688,"diffbotUri":"image|3|854599912","title":"Skill test templates in HackerEarth's library","url":"https://help.hackerearth.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%20from%202023-06-14%2013-48-40.png?width=2064&height=999&name=Screenshot%20from%202023-06-14%2013-48-40.png","naturalWidth":688,"primary":true,"height":333},{"naturalHeight":628,"width":688,"diffbotUri":"image|3|-1874389380","title":"Pre-defined Learning paths in HackerEarth's library","url":"https://help.hackerearth.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Screenshot%20from%202023-07-11%2015-25-34.png?width=2064&height=1884&name=Screenshot%20from%202023-07-11%2015-25-34.png","naturalWidth":688,"height":628}],"originalType":"other","icon":"https://help.hackerearth.com/hubfs/HE_identity.png","diffbotUri":"article|3|1874669168","siteName":"hackerearth.com","type":"article","title":"Upskilling: An overview","tags":[{"score":0.8690615296363831,"sentiment":0.982,"count":7,"label":"UpSkilling","uri":"https://diffbot.com/entity/EPO9Z7liyOV2vYbH5KdlBvg","rdfTypes":["http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Organisation"]}],"breadcrumb":[{"link":"https://help.hackerearth.com/","name":"Help Center"},{"link":"https://help.hackerearth.com/upskilling","name":"Upskilling"}],"humanLanguage":"en","pageUrl":"https://help.hackerearth.com/upskilling-introduction","html":"<p>HackerEarth has introduced Upskilling which allows you to future-proof your tech teams by allowing them to take skill tests in various skills and follow a learning path. It is important to upskill as technology is evolving day-by-day and one needs to be up to date with their skills. Upskilling will help you to keep your team up to date with the latest skills.<\/p>\n<p>Upskilling can cover a wide range of technology-related skills, including programming languages, data analysis, cybersecurity, cloud computing, artificial intelligence, machine learning, and many more. The goal of upskilling is to stay up-to-date with the latest advancements in the field and develop a diverse set of skills that can be applied to different tasks and projects.<\/p>\n<p>Upskilling is particularly important in the technology industry, as new technologies are constantly being developed, and existing technologies are rapidly evolving.

